<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>FAQs - CHAINX</title>
  <link
    rel="stylesheet"
    href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css"
  />
  <style>
    body {
      background: white;
      font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI',
        Roboto, sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 40px 20px;
      color: #333;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background: white;
      padding: 40px;
      border-radius: 15px;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    .header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
      color: #2c3f51;
    }

    .header h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      margin: 0;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.7rem;
      color: #2c3f51;
    }

    .header p {
      margin-top: 10px;
      color: #555;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .faq-list {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 20px;
    }

    .faq-item {
      background-color: #f3f3f3;
      border-left: 5px solid #2c3f51;
      border-radius: 8px;
      overflow: hidden;
      transition: background 0.3s;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    .faq-item:hover {
      background-color: #e9e4f0;
    }

    .faq-question {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 20px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #2c3f51;
      user-select: none;
    }

    .faq-question .icon {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      transition: transform 0.3s ease;
      color: #2c3f51;
    }

    .faq-question.active .icon {
      transform: rotate(180deg);
    }

    .faq-answer {
      max-height: 0;
      overflow: hidden;
      padding: 0 20px;
      color: #555;
      line-height: 1.6;
      transition: max-height 0.3s ease, padding 0.3s ease;
    }

    .faq-answer.active {
      max-height: 500px;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .back-btn {
      display: block;
      width: fit-content;
      margin: 30px auto 0;
      padding: 12px 25px;
      background-color: #1f3a54;
      color: white;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 25px;
      font-size: 16px;
      text-align: center;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background 0.3s ease;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .back-btn:hover {
      background-color: #1c2e40;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      body {
        padding: 20px 10px;
      }

      .container {
        padding: 30px 20px;
      }

      .header h1 {
        font-size: 2rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>
        <i class="fas fa-question-circle"></i> Frequently Asked Questions
      </h1>
      <p>Find answers to common questions about our platform</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-list">
      <div class="faq-item" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
        <div class="faq-question">
          <span>How do I deposit funds?</span>
          <i class="fas fa-chevron-down icon"></i>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          Due to the large amount of information on the platform, users are
          requested to contact customer service to confirm and double-check
          the customer's account information before each deposit. After
          successful recharge, users are requested to provide online customer
          service with a successful transfer slip to update the platform
          account. The payee's name and transfer amount must be consistent
          with the account information provided for immediate payment. If
          users encounter any problems during the deposit process, please
          contact our online customer service for details!
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
        <div class="faq-question">
          <span>How do products work on the platform?</span>
          <i class="fas fa-chevron-down icon"></i>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          The value of product is adjusted according to the market value. The
          product is randomly assigned according to the total balance of the
          user account. The higher the balance of the user account, the higher
          the amount of product, and the higher the profit. If the user is
          worried that the amount of product is too large to afford, please do
          not save too much money to start optimizing.
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
        <div class="faq-question">
          <span>What are the withdrawal hours?</span>
          <i class="fas fa-chevron-down icon"></i>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-answer">Withdrawal time is 10:00 to 22:59 every day.</div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
        <div class="faq-question">
          <span>How does the referral system work?</span>
          <i class="fas fa-chevron-down icon"></i>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          Users can invite new users to become platform users and will receive
          additional referral commissions. The referral fee is an additional
          15%.
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
        <div class="faq-question">
          <span>What are the business hours?</span>
          <i class="fas fa-chevron-down icon"></i>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          Users can optimize the product during the daily operating hours from
          10:00 to 23:00.
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <a href="/" class="back-btn">â¬… Back to home</a>
  </div>

  <script>
    function toggleFaq(element) {
      const question = element.querySelector('.faq-question');
      const answer = element.querySelector('.faq-answer');

      // Close other faq items
      document.querySelectorAll('.faq-item').forEach((item) => {
        if (item !== element) {
          item.querySelector('.faq-question').classList.remove('active');
          item.querySelector('.faq-answer').classList.remove('active');
        }
      });

      // Toggle clicked faq item
      question.classList.toggle('active');
      answer.classList.toggle('active');
    }
  </script>
</body>
</html>
